This release upgrades the Dev Container base image from Ubuntu 24.04 LTS (`noble`) to Ubuntu 26.04 LTS (`resolute`).

The new base image provides a more up-to-date environment with newer versions of preinstalled tools (among others):

* Ubuntu: `24.04.3 LTS` ➜ `26.04 LTS`
* Node.js: `18.19.1` ➜ `22.22.1`
* Git: `2.51.1` ➜ `2.55.0`
* Python: `3.12.3` ➜ `3.14.4`

The updated base image offers access to newer language runtimes and development tools while benefiting from the latest improvements, performance optimizations, and security updates provided by Ubuntu 26.04 LTS.
